    "title": "Moabu na Amoni",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "moabu na amoni",
    "language": "swh",
    "content": "<p>Wamoabu walitokana na Moabu, mwana wa Loti na binti yake mkubwa (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen19:36-Gen19:38\">Mwanzo 19:36–38</a>). Walikaa kwenye uwanda wa juu mashariki mwa Araba. Sehemu kubwa ya Moabu ni ardhi ya juu yenye miteremko laini iliyogawanywa na mabonde. Hata katika kilele chake, Moabu ya kale ilifunika eneo dogo, lakini eneo lake kwenye Barabara ya Mfalme lilikuwa na umuhimu wa kimkakati (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num21:21-Num21:22\">Hesabu 21:21–22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg11:15-Judg11:18\">Waamuzi 11:15–18</a>).</p><p>Kabla ya Waisraeli kuvuka , Wamoabu Ufalme wa Kihashemi wa  Yordani walikuwa chini ya utawala wa Sihoni, mfalme wa Waamori aliyekuwa akitawala Heshboni (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num21:13\">Hesabu 21:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num21:26\">26</a>). Baada ya Waisraeli kumshinda Sihoni, Mfalme Balaki wa Moabu aliogopa kwamba Waisraeli wangeweza kushinda nchi yake, na Moabu akaanzisha vita dhidi yao (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num22:1-Num25:3\">Hesabu 22:1–25:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh24:9\">Yoshua 24:9</a>). Kuanzia wakati huo, Moabu na Waisraeli mara nyingi walikuwa na migogoro (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg3:12-Judg3:30\">Waamuzi 3:12–30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam14:47\">1 Samweli 14:47</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam8:2\">2 Samweli 8:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs3:1-2Kgs3:27\">2 Wafalme 3</a>). Hata hivyo, kulikuwa pia na nyakati za amani kati yao (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth1:1-Ruth1:2\">Ruthu 1:1–2</a>). Mwanamke Mmoabu aitwaye Ruthu alionyesha wema mkubwa kwa mama mkwe wake Mwisraeli, Naomi, aliyepitia misiba mingi. Ruthu alikua sehemu ya ukoo uliozaa Mfalme Daudi na Yesu.</p><p>Waamoni walikuwa wazao wa mwana wa binti mdogo wa Lutu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen19:36-Gen19:38\">Mwanzo 19:36–38</a>). Walikaa katika eneo la Ufalme wa Kihashemi wa Yordani, kaskazini mashariki mwa Araba. Waisraeli walipofika baada ya kuondoka Misri, Mungu aliwaambia wasichukue ardhi ya Waamoni, kwani ilikuwa ya wazao wa Lutu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut2:18-Deut2:19\">Kumbukumbu la Torati 2:18–19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut2:37\">37</a>). Waamoni waliwasaidia Wamoabi kupigana dhidi ya Israeli na walizuiwa kujiunga na kusanyiko la Bwana kwa vizazi kumi (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut23:3-Deut23:6\">Kumbukumbu la Torati 23:3–6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh13:1-Neh13:2\">Nehemia 13:1–2</a>; angalia <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num22:1-Num25:3\">Hesabu 22:1–25:3</a>). Baada ya hapo, Waamoni mara nyingi walipigana na Israeli (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg10:1-Judg11:40\">Waamuzi 10–11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam11:1-1Sam11:15\">1 Samweli 11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam14:47\">14:47</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr20:1-1Chr20:3\">1 Mambo ya Nyakati 20:1–3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr20:1-2Chr20:24\">2 Mambo ya Nyakati 20:1–24</a>). Hata hivyo, Daudi alionekana kuwa na ushirikiano nao kwa muda fulani (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam17:27-2Sam17:29\">2 Samweli 17:27–29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam23:37\">23:37</a>).</p><p><u>Sehemu za Kujifunza Zaidi</u></p><p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut23:3-Deut23:6\">Kumbukumbu la Torati 23:3–6</a></p>",
